  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Rinse the tempeh and crumble it into small pieces.",
    "In a small saucepan, heat the olive oil over low heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1-2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the pickle relish, lemon juice, oregano, salt, and pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 2-3 minutes until slightly thickened.",
    "Stir in the cashew cream until smooth.",
    "Transfer the tempeh to a ramekin and spoon the sauce over the top.",
    "Sprinkle the nutritional yeast over the sauce.",
    "Bake the tempeh in the preheated oven for 20-25 minutes until golden brown.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
  ],
